ABUJA- Dr. Folasade Yemi-Esan, Head of the Civil Service of the Federation (HCSF), has directed civil servants on Grade Level 12 and below to stay and work from home in view of the second wave of COVID-19 pandemic. In a circular made available to Daily Independent on Tuesday in Abuja, Yemi-Esan said this directive was sequel to the approval of the recommendations of the Presidential Task Force(PTF) on COVID-19 by President Muhammadu Buhari. The circular signed by Yemi-Esan said in the light of the second wave of infections in Nigeria, that officers on Grade Level 12 and below are expected to stay at home for a period of five weeks, effective from Wednesday, December 23, 2020 and wait for further directive. EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! According to her, “This has become necessary to streamline the number of officers that come to work daily. Notwithstanding, the affected officers are expected to perform their duties from home.” “Meanwhile, in reporting to their offices for duty, officers on GL 13 and above are to adhere to other preventive measures including the maintenance of physical distancing, regular washing and/or sanitizing of hands, wearing of face masks and reducing the number of visitors.” Delta Exco Approves Construction Of 13 Roads, Flyover Makinde Harps On Zero Tolerance For Corruption, Inaugurates State’s Agency “Furthermore. in line with the prescription of the PTF, virtual meetings are to be encouraged in offices with a view to minimizing physical contact.” “In addition, Permanent Secretaries and Chief Executive Officers are expected to sustain the provision and use of necessary amenities in compliance with the existing guidelines on prevention of the spread of the pandemic.” Yemi-Esan directed security operatives manning the gates to offices to demand identity cards of staff coming to the office to ensure that they are on GL 13 and above before granting them access to the premises. She further urged the Permanent Secretaries and Chief Executive Officers to bring the contents of this circular to the attention of all concerned and ensure compliance. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION